<p><strong>NBC - Who We Are</strong>: Nazlawi Business College is a modern and progressive Qualification Awarding College devoted to Specialist Accountants in Sudan. Nazlawi Business College is the first College in the Middle East &amp; Africa approved by the Sudan Ministry of Education to offer courses for specialist Accountants in Project Accountancy, Corporate Accountancy, and Project Management. In addition to our Ministry of Education approval we are an Accountants Institute Approved Business School.</p>
<p><strong>NBC - Vision and Mission</strong>: Our vision is to be the most influential Accountants College in Sudan, providing our students and graduates with a primary resource for high-value qualifications, training, events, peer integration, and career progression. We provide high-quality support and service to our students and graduates during their quest to become Specialist Accountants enabling them to add value to their organizations. We achieve this with a passionate belief in all our students and their ability to learn.</p>
<p><strong>NBC - What We Do</strong>: Nazlawi Business College is a business college focused on delivering high quality education to students in Accountancy, Corporate and Project Governance, and Project Management. We leverage the expertise and enthusiasm of our lecturers to deliver meaningful and valuable education to our students throughout Sudan. As a Ministry of Education Approved College, and Accountants Institute Approved Business School we offer high quality courses covering a range of subjects specific to Accountancy, Governance and Project Management.</p>
<p><strong>NBC - Our Accreditation</strong>: Nazlawi Business College is approved to offer Qualifications by the Sudan Ministry of Higher Education and we have been recognized by Accountants Institute as an Approved Business School for over five years. We understand the needs of our students and graduates, and the importance of offering them valuable and meaningful education that delivers high-class qualifications. That is why we have invested heavily into gaining recognition by the Sudan Ministry of Education, and engaging with an international Professional Membership Body such as Accountants Institute.</p>
<p><strong>Nazlawi Business College - Courses:</strong></p>
<p>NBC Bachelor Degree in Project Accounting: In order for an organization to ensure that it has sound Project Governance in place it needs to have highly-skilled people available who understand; Governance, Corporate Management, and Project Management. Nazlawi Business College provides the learning environment to enable students to become skilled in the subjects that are required to perform effectively as Project Governors. We provide a structured set of modules that enable you to progress your learning through the spectrum of topics that are required to gain our Bachelor Degree in Project Accounting, professional Certificate in Project Accounting and Certified Project Accountant ACPA which will enable you to become a Senior Member of your organization. Note: Completion of this degree enables the student to apply to join Accountants Institute as an RQA Registered Qualified Accountant with Accountants Institute.</p>
<p>NBC Bachelor Degree in Corporate Accounting: Implementing and maintaining an effective Corporate Governance framework - in any organization - requires highly-skilled people who understand; Governance, Corporate Management, and the peculiarities of the organization itself. Nazlawi Business College provides the environment to enable students to become skilled in the subjects that are required to perform effectively as Corporate Governors. We provide a structured set of modules that enable you to progress your learning through the spectrum of topics that are required to gain our Bachelor Degree in Corporate Accounting, Professional Certificate in Corporate Accounting and Certified Corporate Accountant ACCEA enabling you to add value as a Senior Member of your organization. Note: Completion of this degree enables the student to apply to join Accountants Institute as an RQA Registered Qualified Accountant with Accountants Institute.</p>
<p>Join as an NBC Student</p>
<p>NBC Students Access to Accountants Institute Membership: Upon enrolment NBC students will become an &ldquo;Affiliate Member&rdquo; of Accountants Institute and Nazlawi business College. Upon successful completion of Year Two Affiliate Member will become &nbsp;a Professional Qualifications certificate in Technical Accounting and &nbsp;Membership GAT Gradate Accounting Technicians with NBC and&nbsp; able to apply for membership as &ldquo;GAT Graduate Accounting Technician with Accountants Institute&rdquo;. Graduate Accounting Technicians successfully completing Year Three will become a Professional Qualifications Certificate in Advanced Technical Accounting and Membership AAT Advanced Accounting Technicians with NBC and entitled to apply to the Accountants Institute for membership as a &ldquo;QAT Qualified Accounting Technician with Accountants Institute&rdquo;. Advanced&nbsp; Accounting Technician, after completing Year Four in &nbsp;Project Accounting , will become &nbsp;a Bachelor Degree in Project Accounting with Professional Qualifications&nbsp; Certificate&nbsp; in Project Accounting&nbsp; and ACPA Certified Project Accountant with NBC and&nbsp; entitled to apply Accountants Institute to become RQA Registered Qualified Accountant with Accountants Institute.</p>
<p>Advanced&nbsp; Accounting Technician, after completing Year Four in Corporate Accounting&nbsp; , will become&nbsp; a bachelor Degree in Corporate&nbsp; Accounting&nbsp; with Professional Qualifications&nbsp; Certificates&nbsp; in Corporate Accounting&nbsp; and ACCEA Certified Corporate Accountant with NBC and&nbsp; entitled to apply Accountants Institute to become RQA Registered Qualified Accountant with Accountants Institute.</p>
